# isla

10-K Item Segmentation with Line-based Attention (ISLA) is a tool to process
EDGAR 10-K reports and extract item-specific text. 


[![PyPI - Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/isla.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/isla)
[![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/isla.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/isla)

-----

**Table of Contents**

- [Installation](#installation)
- [License](#license)

## Installation

```console
pip install isla
```

